# 02 — Brand & Voice

## Visual Personality
**Dark Luxury Minimalism.** A blend of Apple (clarity), Linear (precision), Stripe (craft), and Vercel (technical confidence).

## Brand Keywords (lean into these)
Premium · Precise · Technical · Intelligent · Confident · Futuristic · Human.

## Anti-Keywords (never evoke)
Cyberpunk · gaming · hacker terminal · neon overload · sci-fi movie set. No "matrix rain", no glitch text, no chrome-robot tropes.

## Voice & Tone
- **Confident, not hypey.** State outcomes plainly. Let the value speak.
- **Technical but human.** We respect the reader's intelligence; we never talk down.
- **Editorial, not salesy.** Short, declarative sentences. White space in the language as well as the layout.
- **Urgent without panic.** Scarcity is real and stated calmly (seats remaining, countdown), never with fake red-alert spam.

### Voice examples
```
❌ "🚀 Unlock the SECRET to AI riches!! Limited time ONLY!!!"
✅ "Build an AI employee in three hours. Then put it to work."

❌ "Our revolutionary cutting-edge platform leverages synergies."
✅ "You'll wire a real agent to Telegram and Gmail. Live."
```

## Naming & Capitalization
- Product/event names render exactly: **NeuralVarsity**, **Agentic AI Masterclass**, **Build Your First AI Employee**.
- Use sentence case for body copy and most UI; reserve display-case impact for hero/section headlines.
- Currency always `₹` glyph, no space: `₹109`.

## Logo / Wordmark
Wordmark-first (typographic). No mascots, no robot icons. If a mark is used, it is geometric, monochrome on dark, and never animated gratuitously.

## Imagery Doctrine
Prefer typography, negative space, and the single 3D AI Core over photography. No stock photos. Any real photo (instructor, testimonial video poster) must be high-quality, color-graded toward the dark palette, and intentional.

## Emotional Arc (what the brand should make people feel)
Curiosity → recognition ("this is the shift") → capability ("I can build this") → urgency ("reserve now"). Brand never sells fear of AI; it sells **agency over AI**.
